Title: Home
Plot: A baby is found buried alive in shallow ground and appears to have birth defects resulting from generations of inbreeding, leading Mulder and Scully to a reclusive family who have a history of inbred children.
GuestStars: Tucker Smallwood, Sebastian Spence, Chris Norris, John Trottier, Karin Konoval, Judith Maxie, Kenny James, Lachlan Murdoch, Neil Denis, Cory Frye, Douglas Smith, Adrian Hughes
